SELECT
  timestamp_sensor AS "time",
  COUNT(*) AS "metric"
FROM
  etlocationuser

WHERE user_id IN ($user_id )
GROUP BY
  timestamp_sensor
ORDER BY
  timestamp_sensor;

SELECT
  timestamp_sensor AS "time",
  x1 AS "x",
  y1 AS "y",
  uncertain
FROM
  etlocationuser
WHERE

ORDER BY
  timestamp_sensor

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    x1, 
    x2, 
    y1, 
    y2, 
    SUM(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM timestamp_sensor)) as "time"
FROM 
    etlocationuser
    WHERE
    user_id IN ($user_id )
GROUP BY 
    x1, 
    x2, 
    y1, 
    y2

data.series.map((s) => {
  console.log("series", s);
  if (s.refId === "P1") {
    p1Values =
      s.fields.find((f) => f.name === "P1").values.buffer ||
      s.fields.find((f) => f.name === "P1").values;
  }
});

// Calcula la media de los valores de P1

panels.title: HeatMap

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  FLOOR(x1) as x1,
  FLOOR(x2) as x2,
  FLOOR(y1) as y1,
  FLOOR(y2) as y2,

  COUNT(*) as count
FROM
  etlocationuser
WHERE
  timestamp_sensor >= NOW() - INTERVAL '30 day'
GROUP BY
  FLOOR(x1),
  FLOOR(x2),
